IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User james.nvc@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.passwd/gmail.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns Inbox ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
